                           "The Client remains liable for any unpaid fees and charges. Notice: Any notice or other communication required or permitted to be given under this Agreement will be given in writing and will be deemed effective on the day delivered in person, or the business day after the day on which such notice was mailed registered or certified mail, postage prepaid, addressed as follows:",
                           "Source: visit_visa_governing_law_and_dispute_resolution.php",
                           "Governing Law \u0026 Dispute Resolution In the event of any dispute, controversy or claim arising out of or relating to the Agreement, or the breach, termination, or invalidity thereof, or as to any related claim in restitution or at law, in equity or pursuant to any statute (collectively referred to as \u0027\"Disputes\"), the aggrieved Party undertakes to cause a written notice to the other Party to initiate discussions.",
                           "Both parties agree to discuss the dispute with the aim of reaching a solution amicably within 30 (Thirty) calendar days from the date of the first notice (said written notice) intimating the cause of the Disputes. If a solution is reached between the Parties by discussion, the same shall be documented and signed by both the Parties.",
                           "Both parties agree that, if the dispute is not settled as per the above-mentioned clause, both the parties have a right to seek the appropriate remedy before the civil court and consumer courts for breach of contract, recovery and damages.",
                           "Both the parties agreed that, the nature of contract entered by the parties in this agreement shall not constitute any criminal offence in case of breach contract.",
