                           "Failure to Obtain Work Permit After JOL If DM CONSULTANTS or a third-party agent successfully obtains a JOL for the Client but is unable to secure the Work Permit apart from those reasons mentioned in Clause I, the Client is entitled to a refund of 50%the amount paid for JOL/stage 2.",
                           "Source: refund_procedures_and_conditions.php",
                           "REFUND PROCEDURES AND CONDITIONS Completion of Refund Formalities Refunds, where applicable, will be processed only after the completion of all formalities, including management approval, and the deduction of relevant charges (e.g., VAT/GST if applicable credit card processing fees at 2.5%, and administrative fees).",
                           "Refund Processing Time The estimated Turnaround Time (TAT) for processing refunds is 45 working days from the date of signing the refund declaration.",
